-- Hungarian Magyar Posta buys 49 pct stake in FHB commercial bank
-- 
-- Tue Sep 30, 2014 03:32PM EDT
-- None



BUDAPEST, Sept 30 (Reuters) - Hungary's national postal company Magyar Posta has bought a 49 percent stake in FHB Kereskedelmi Bank for 28.5 billion Hungarian forints, mortgage bank FHB said in a statement on the Budapest bourse's website on Tuesday.

